{
  "texts": [
    "Second, the interviews were carried out after students' one-time interactions with the system developed by the research team, which may not fully reveal different perceptions as interactions with the system change over evolutionary timescales (Kim et al., 2022; Kim, 2023).",
    "Future studies could be conducted with a longitudinal design in an actual classroom setting and explore students' perceptions at different time periods of GenAI-assisted writing.",
    "Furthermore, future research can utilize qualitative data analysis (QDA) software (e.g., NVivo, Atlas.ti, MAXQDA), or text-mining techniques for alternative data analysis and interpretation.",
    "• Use appropriate paragraphing.",
    "• Use a diverse vocabulary to convey precise meanings (e.g., instead of \"big,\" use \"enormous\" or \"massive\")."
  ]
}